提交的机密简报中提出了这一问题。布卢门撒尔和布莱克本写道：“TikTok 是中国政府手中的武器，对我们的民主制度和国家安全构成了积极的风险。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3janOi&quot;>;上周，以异常迅速的速度在此过程中，众议院&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/15/24102472/house-tiktok-ban-bill-staffers-calls-congress&quot;>;通过了一项法案&lt;/a>; ...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/22/24108674/tiktok-ban-classified-intelligence-briefing-china-national-security&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/22/24108674/tiktok-ban-classified-intelligence-briefing-china-national-security" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/22/24108674/tiktok-ban-classified-intelligence-briefing-china-national-security</id><author><name>佐藤米亚</name></author></entry></feed>